      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-B-00001-000-00010-R"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Die</hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="org" ref="#pmb29626">Zeit</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><hi rend="italics"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></hi></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1904-11-27">27. XI. 04</date>.</seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>er Tageszeitung</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="italics"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb120">I. Wipplingerstrasse 38</rs></hi></hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">Herausgeber:</hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Prof. Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12790">I. Singer</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11867">Heinrich Kanner</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Feuilleton-Redaktion</hi></hi></seg></opener><p><salute>Lieber,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03458-1"/>wenn Sie
               schon da sind, könnten wir uns vielleicht bald einmal sehen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03458-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> war am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1904-11-24" subtype="date-only"/> aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs> zurückgekehrt. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2167">Salten</rs> sah er nachweislich am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1904-11-29" subtype="date-only"/>
                  wieder.</note>? Ich bin sehr allein, und – überhaupt.</p><closer>herzlich Ihr <signed>Salten</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
